  "text": "No abnormal changes in estrous cycle, sperm parameters and necropsy findings were observed at any dose tested. The significant increase of absolute spleen weight observed in males of the 500 mg/kg/day group was not considered treatment-related due to lack of supportive serum biochemical and histopathological findings, and was within the limits of normal reference data [CITATION_1] .",
